## 4. Layout Rules

### 4.1 Full Width

- **Remove** `max-w-6xl`, `max-w-7xl` constraints
- Use `px-6` for consistent horizontal padding
- Allow content to fill available width

```svelte
<!-- Page container -->
<div class="min-h-full bg-gray-950 text-slate-50 p-6 overflow-y-auto">
    <!-- Content without max-width -->
</div>
```

### 4.2 Scrolling

- Use `min-h-full` instead of `h-full` for proper scrolling
- Add `overflow-y-auto` on page containers
- Main layout handles overflow with `flex flex-col min-h-screen`

### 4.3 Grid Layouts

```svelte
<!-- Responsive card grid -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-5">
    <!-- Cards -->
</div>
```

