## 6. Prohibited Patterns

### 6.1 DO NOT USE

```css
/* Light backgrounds */
❌ bg-white, bg-gray-50, bg-slate-50

/* Backdrop blur (glossy effect) */
❌ backdrop-blur-sm, backdrop-blur

/* Light mode specific styles */
❌ dark:hidden with light variants

/* Fixed max-width on page containers */
❌ max-w-6xl mx-auto (unless specifically needed)

/* Overly bright shadows */
❌ shadow-2xl (without black tint)
```

### 6.2 DO USE

```css
/* Dark backgrounds */
✅ bg-gray-950, bg-slate-900/80

/* Subtle depth with shadows */
✅ shadow-lg shadow-black/20

/* Semi-transparent layers */
✅ bg-slate-800/50, border-slate-700/50

/* Full-width with padding */
✅ px-6 (no max-width)
```

